quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  22,39,Udhina Lilladhīna Yuqātalūna Bi'annahum Žulimū Wa 'Inna Allāha `Alá Naşrihim Laqadīrun
  22,40,Al-Ladhīna 'Ukhrijū Min Diyārihim Bighayri Ĥaqqin 'Illā 'An Yaqūlū Rabbunā Allāhu Wa Lawlā Daf`u Allāhi An-Nāsa Ba`đahum Biba`đin Lahuddimat Şawāmi`u Wa Biya`un Wa Şalawātun Wa Masājidu Yudhkaru Fīhā Asmu Allāhi Kathīrāan Wa Layanşuranna Allāhu Man Yanşuruhu 'Inna Allāha Laqawīyun `Azīzun
  22,41,Al-Ladhīna 'In Makkannāhum Fī Al-'Arđi 'Aqāmū Aş-Şalāata Wa 'Ātaw Az-Zakāata Wa 'Amarū Bil-Ma`rūfi Wa Nahaw `Ani Al-Munkari Wa Lillahi `Āqibatu Al-'Umūri
  22,42,Wa 'In Yukadhibūka Faqad Kadhabat Qablahum Qawmu Nūĥin Wa `Ādun Wa Thamūdu
  22,43,Wa Qawmu 'Ibrāhīma Wa Qawmu Lūţin
  22,44,Wa 'Aşĥābu Madyana Wa Kudhiba Mūsá Fa'amlaytu Lilkāfirīna Thumma 'Akhadhtuhum Fakayfa Kāna Nakīri
  22,45,Faka'ayyin Min Qaryatin 'Ahlaknāhā Wa Hiya Žālimatun Fahiya Khāwiyatun `Alá `Urūshihā Wa Bi'rin Mu`aţţalatin Wa Qaşrin Mashīdin
  22,46,Afalam Yasīrū Fī Al-'Arđi Fatakūna Lahum Qulūbun Ya`qilūna Bihā 'Aw 'Ādhānun Yasma`ūna Bihā Fa'innahā Lā Ta`má Al-'Abşāru Wa Lakin Ta`má Al-Qulūbu Allatī Fī Aş-Şudūri